        public static DataSourceInfo getDataSourceInfo(java.io.File file)
                                        throws java.io.IOException
        Returns a data source info definition from an xml file with the properties xml format and standard keys:
        • data-source-name
        • server-name
        • port-number
        • database
        • user
        • password

        Returns:
